        <detaileddescription>
<para>Handles received Solicitation PDU RPL Status messages from a Solicitation PDU RPL server.The <computeroutput>start</computeroutput> param represents the start of range that server has cleared. The <computeroutput>length</computeroutput> param represents length of range cleared by server.</para>
